text.tspan: Confrontation - I will not stand by, I will work to end you.
Sacrifice - I am a small cog, but perhaps I can set things in motion.
Stasis - The system isn't so bad, let's just keep it going.
Complacency - It's not my concern, It's not my concern, It's not...
Destruction - It's all fucked, just blow it all up.
Ascension - If you can't beat 'em, join 'em.
Escape - Screw it, I'm getting out of here. You're all on your own.
Acceleration - If we've got to burn, let's burn hot.
